{"tid":1549325,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［阿叔］［追擊港澳辦］國民教育民意調查","createTime":"2019-09-07T09:32:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T18:33:03.000Z","uid":35215,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"dbc5b5fbb0e0fa35425c1b0d8d3eff884b4d8e02","tid":1549325,"uid":35215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:32:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">上次阿叔就《逃犯條例》民意研究，24小時之內收集咗 6779 份問卷！</span><br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1544873/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1544873/page/1</a></span><br />\n<br />\n首先好多謝大家一直以嚟嘅支持，令我哋喺咁短時間之內就收到咁多嘅回應，用數字話俾政府同社會聽，<span style=\"color: orange;\">單單係撤回，香港人並唔收貨。</span><br />\n我地希望直接用數據去抗衡香港政權嘅fake news。嚟緊，我哋將會籌辦一系列針對政權嘅民調，希望大家支持。詳文如下：<br />\n<br />\n近日，國務院港澳辦發言人就香港局勢發表意見，認為特區政府應把國民教育列為重要的工作。為此，「眾意院」希望透過一份廣泛且具公信力的民意調查，向社會反映市民大眾對國民教育的看法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/DTbP4ZnVS7KQggbN9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FDTbP4ZnVS7KQggbN9&d=59R0jsXjdYUW2Qgfgwt6uL4BfDbUEiSkD5bB26vbFoA%3D&h=32ed427e\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/DTbP4ZnVS7KQggbN9</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">為什麼我們關心國民教育？</span></span><br />\n自政府於2012年首次提出設立國民教育，社會一直為止爭議不休&mdash;&mdash;支持一方不斷強調國民教育有助培養學生對國家的熱愛和認同感；反對一方則擔心偏頗的教材會變相政治洗腦，直接促成2012的反國教運動。在社會撕裂的當下，若政府貿然重推國民教育，幾可肯定會引發新一輪的社會衝突。為此，我們希望探討大家關於政治及國民教育的看法。<br />\n<br />\n為此，我們希望透過民意調查搜集社會大眾就政治意識及國民教育的看法，希望大家可以積極參與，令民意調查更能反映真實民意。亦請留意我哋嘅facebook page同官網，以參與將來嘅民調，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/KongPollster/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FKongPollster%2F&d=59R0jsXjdYUW2Qgfgwt6uL4BfDbUEiSkD5bB26vbFoA%3D&h=0da222cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/KongPollster/</a><br />\nOfficial Site:<a href=\"https://kongpollster.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkongpollster.com%2F&d=59R0jsXjdYUW2Qgfgwt6uL4BfDbUEiSkD5bB26vbFoA%3D&h=87608319\" target=\"_blank\">https://kongpollster.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n阿叔以前嘅post:<br />\n【罷課不罷學・有片有真相】邊個話學生唔了解中國所以先唔愛國？<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1531298\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1531298</a>"},{"pid":"6b3c34f16cbd5674fd66d5cfa6d5ed88cf4045ee","tid":1549325,"uid":166947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:33:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8ebeac56b132d6649bdbad4bb929637521e49914","tid":1549325,"uid":35215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b3c34f16cbd5674fd66d5cfa6d5ed88cf4045ee","tid":1549325,"uid":166947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:33:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:36:16.000Z","msg":"多謝支持"},{"pid":"8a2651e78e9a4c96e8e0b1a323c01536772b2bd7","tid":1549325,"uid":162478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:40:31.000Z","msg":"keep going"},{"pid":"415e4c419050fd1dffd89fa936414c14c3bd9c6f","tid":1549325,"uid":251458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:40:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d71dbc71f32e01b2e3dfaeba54e7fa671c57406f","tid":1549325,"uid":251458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:40:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"600e3390107f50dde44fa76a57a5975f043e091b","tid":1549325,"uid":22833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:41:15.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"0067d43fd5367fb5ef06e2c2ae7dab2eb8d7267e","tid":1549325,"uid":11607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:41:21.000Z","msg":"阿叔加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c6ca49f6730cb975a1ed1fea00edb2906a12324","tid":1549325,"uid":33716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:41:23.000Z","msg":"推到核爆"},{"pid":"0cfe4b5f6a56d03d221cbe67e4feeb8b59359284","tid":1549325,"uid":188671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019